您好！我不明白您说的“我不明白我的人民的”是什么意思。您能更详细地解释一下您想了解什么吗？
(Nín hǎo! Wǒ bù míngbái nín shuō de “wǒ bù míngbái wǒ de rénmín de” shì shénme yìsi. Nín néng gèng xiángxì de jiěshì yīxià nín xiǎng liǎojiě shénme ma?)
(Hello! I don't understand what you mean by "I don't understand my people's". Can you explain in more detail what you would like to know?)
